{
 "name": "RPlog_Renaissance_of_Innovation",
 "title": "Renaissance of Innovation",
 "summary": "In the renovated Council Chambers of Union Hall in Plaxton, the Caspian Union gathers for the launch of the 'Second Renaissance of Innovation,' a grand civic and economic initiative. The Presav Crestian presides over the proceedings, attended by figures including the doctor Lynae Cassius, the Grand Admiral Axel, the Presav Elana Tracer, the eccentric engineer Druze, and the pilot Nara. The event celebrates Caspar's renewed outward-looking ambition and innovation under the new Union, blending political ceremony with the personal currents running among its prominent attendees.",
